title: Golf Course Locations, Washington DC,
name: Golf Course Locations, Washington DC,
description:
Golf Course locations. The dataset contains locations and attributes of Golf Courses, created as part of the DC Geographic Information System (DC GIS) for the D.C. Office of the Chief Technology Officer (OCTO) and participating D.C. government agencies.

A database researched by the DC Office of the Chief Technology Officer (OCTO) identified Golf Course locations and DC GIS staff geo-processed the data.

author.source: DC Office of the Chief Technology Officer (OCTO)
